mmj.gmff

Class GMFFFileFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • mmj.gmff.GMFFFileFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.FileFilter

    public class GMFFFileFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.FileFilter
    GMFFFileFilter is used by the GMFFFolder to select Proof Worksheet files for export from a GMFFFolder.

    It is used by GMFFFolder but is called by Java via the File method listFiles(fileFilter). call.

        public boolean accept(java.io.File pathname)
        FileFilter for MMT Folders.

        Return true if:

        • entry in directory is readable file, and

        • (namePrefix.compareToIgnoreCase( lowestNamePrefix) >= 0)
